text: KCBP (95.5 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Westley, California. The station is owned by Modesto Peace/Life Center and airs a community radio format. The station was assigned the KCBP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on April 6, 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * CBP Category:Radio stations established in 2018 Category:2018 establishments in California Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Stanislaus County, California
